Summary: ES Web Browser
Name: esnavigator
Version: @VERSION@
Release: 1%{?dist}
License: Apache License, Version 2.0
Group: Applications/Internet
URL: http://code.google.com/p/es-operating-system/
Source0: esnavigator-%{version}.tar.gz
Buildroot: %{_tmppath}/%{name}-%{version}-%{release}-root
BuildRequires: bison js-devel v8-devel re2c libicu-devel freetype-devel freeglut-devel giflib-devel libpng-devel libjpeg-devel boost-devel boost-iostreams boost-system boost-regex ipa-gothic-fonts ipa-mincho-fonts ipa-pgothic-fonts ipa-pmincho-fonts gdouros-aegean-fonts
BuildRequires: esidl

%description
ES web browser is a new web browser, including a totally new CSS/HTML
rendering engine, currently being developed as a part of the ES 
operating system project.
The ES web browser core components will be used like a window system
in today's operating systems in the ES operating system, but before
doing so, we are experimenting it as a standalone web browser on Linux.

